sequenceDiagram
    actor C as Customer
    participant LW as Livewire (CheckoutPage)
    participant BE as Backend (Laravel)
    participant MT as Midtrans
    participant Q as Queue
    participant FA as Filament Admin
    participant BT as Biteship
    participant WA as WhatsApp

    Note over C,WA: === Fase Checkout ===

    C->>LW: Checkout (Pickup/Delivery) — cart sudah diisi dari katalog
    LW->>BE: Livewire checkout()
    BE->>BE: Validasi stok
    BE->>BE: Reservasi stok (lockForUpdate)
    BE->>BE: Generate Order Number (ALBA-YYYYMMDD-XXX)
    BE->>BE: Hitung total + shipping
    BE->>MT: Request Snap Token (server-side)
    MT-->>BE: Snap Token
    BE-->>LW: Order created (status: pending) + Snap Token

    Note over C,WA: === Fase Pembayaran ===

    LW->>MT: Customer bayar via Snap popup
    MT-->>MT: Proses pembayaran

    MT->>BE: Webhook: POST /api/webhook/midtrans
    BE->>BE: Verifikasi IP Whitelist
    BE->>BE: Verifikasi Signature Key
    BE-->>MT: HTTP 200 OK
    BE->>Q: Dispatch ProcessMidtransWebhook

    Q->>Q: Job: GET /v2/{order_id}/status (verifikasi sekunder)
    Q->>MT: MidtransService::getOrderStatus()
    MT-->>Q: Status confirmed
    Q->>BE: Update order.status to Settlement
    Q->>BE: Insert order_status_logs
    Q->>BE: Kurangi stock fisik (deduct_reserved)

    Note over C,WA: === Fase Admin Proses (via Filament) ===

    FA->>BE: Admin klik "Proses" (OrderResource action)
    BE->>BE: TransitionOrderStatus → Processing

    Note over C,WA: === Jalur Pickup ===

    FA->>BE: Admin klik "Siap Diambil"
    BE->>BE: TransitionOrderStatus → ReadyPickup
    BE->>Q: Dispatch SendWhatsAppNotification
    Q->>WA: Job: Kirim WhatsApp "Siap Diambil"
    WA-->>C: Pesan WhatsApp
    FA->>BE: Admin klik "Selesai"
    BE->>BE: TransitionOrderStatus → Completed

    Note over C,WA: === Jalur Delivery (Biteship) ===

    FA->>BE: Admin klik "Kirim" (auto-create Biteship order)
    BE->>BT: Create order + request pickup
    BT-->>BE: waybill_id + courier info
    BE->>BE: Insert shipments + TransitionOrderStatus → Shipping

    BT->>BE: Webhook: POST /api/webhook/biteship
    BE->>BE: Verifikasi Signature + IP
    BE-->>BT: HTTP 200 OK
    BE->>Q: Dispatch ProcessBiteshipWebhook

    Q->>BE: Update shipment.tracking_status
    Q->>BE: Sync order.status to Delivered (jika delivered)
    Q->>WA: Job: Kirim WhatsApp "Pesanan Sampai"
    WA-->>C: Pesan WhatsApp

    Note over C,WA: === Fase Selesai ===

    FA->>BE: Admin klik "Selesai" / auto
    BE->>BE: TransitionOrderStatus → Completed
    BE-->>FA: Pesanan selesai
